_3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmUMHmlfzt_text","label":"ggmUMHmlfzt_text","default":"<p>It’s not magic—<strong>it’s the body finally getting what it needs to rebuild from within</strong>. Unlike creams that rinse off at the end of the day, this kind of support sticks with you. The results show up in the mirror, sure—but even more in how you&nbsp;feel day to day. <strong>More comfort. More confidence. More energy to show up as yourself.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkmtPJdmK0_text","label":"ggkmtPJdmK0_text","default":"7. It Supports the Whole You."},{"type":"html","id":"ggt5trgs_C5_text","label":"ggt5trgs_C5_text","default":"<p>This isn’t just another beauty fix—<strong>it’s a daily wellness tool designed with&nbsp;real women in mind</strong>. It supports the full picture of aging: physical changes, hormonal shifts, and everything in between.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3vGvIMqvd_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg3vGvIMqvd_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/7_3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1IqMe2L0w_text","label":"gg1IqMe2L0w_text","default":"<p>With every capsule, she’s not trying to look 25—<strong>she’s fueling vitality, strength, and balance from the inside out</strong>. It’s for the woman who wants to keep showing up for her life, her way—no filters, no fluff. Just something that helps her feel like&nbsp;herself again.</p>"}],
